    "type": "Question",
    "name": "Question 43 @ 2019/2020",
    "Question": {
      "content": "Two series capacitors (2μF and unknown) charged from 24V. The 2μF capacitor reaches 16V, the other 8V. Find the unknown capacitance.",
      "type": "OBJ",
      "options": [
        "1μF",
        "2μF",
        "4μF",
        "8μF"
      ]
    },
    "Answer": {
      "type": "string",
      "content": "4μF"
    },
    "Explanation": {
      "type": "string",
      "content": "In series, charges are equal: \\(Q = C_1V_1 = C_2V_2\\). Thus, \\((2\\mu F)(16V) = C_2(8V)\\) → \\(C_2 = 4\\mu F\\)."
    },
